						               													<description>Larceny is a heist-themed party game for 3+ players. Gather your crew, pick the Score and plan your heist!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round one player is the Chief, everyone else is the Crew. The Chief draws a Score from the deck. This card is what the Crew is stealing during the heist. The Chief then draws two Catches, which are problems that crop up during the heist.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Crew now has to play Fix cards from their hand to try to over come the Catches. Once everyone has played a Fix on each Catch, the Chief decides which Fix is the best, and points are awarded. Next round someone else is the Chief, and play continues.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Larceny has numerous variant gameplay modes. Most notable are the versus Troubleshooters mode, the cooperative Heist mode, the strategic planning Black Bag mode, and the narrative Best Laid Plan mode.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
